'''2014年4月阿布加炸彈爆炸事件'''是2014年4月14日早上發生在[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]首都[[阿布加|阿布加]]的[[恐怖攻擊|恐怖攻擊]]事件。當日早上6:45，兩枚炸彈在阿布加市中心西南{{convert|8|km|mi}}擁擠的公車站爆炸，造成至少75人罹難，124人受傷<ref name="AP1">{{Cite web| url = http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/A/AF_NIGERIA_EXPLOSION?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT| title = MINISTER: 75 DEAD IN BLAST AT NIGERIAN BUS STATION| date = 15 April 2014| accessdate = 15 April 2014| publisher = Associated Press| archive-date = 2014-04-16| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140416192342/http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/A/AF_NIGERIA_EXPLOSION?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27018751 | title = Nigeria violence: 'Seventy killed' in Abuja bus blasts | publisher = BBC News | accessdate = 14 April 2014 | date = 14 April 2014 | archive-date = 2021-01-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210104152354/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27018751 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27018751 | title = Nigeria violence: 'Seventy killed' in Abuja bus blasts | publisher = [[英國廣播公司新聞網|英國廣播公司新聞網]] | accessdate = 2014-04-14 | date = 2014-04-14 | language = en | archive-date = 2021-01-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210104152354/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27018751 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=WSJ1>{{cite news | last1 = Ijagba | first1 = Gbenga Seun | first2 = Drew | last2 = Hinshaw | title = Nigeria Bomb Blast Kills At Least 71 | url = http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303663604579500971757800310 | accessdate = 2014-04-14 | newspaper = [[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]] | date = 2014-04-14 | location = [[阿布加|阿布加]] | language = en | archive-date = 2014-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140529011130/http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303663604579500971757800310 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=ChannelS1>{{cite news|title=Bomb Blast Rocks Crowded Nyanya 